{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290190/extras/Discord.gif?t=1725479401\" /><br><br>Lt Blitz has the city  sieged, and it's your job to destroy his troops. Shoot, dodge and upgrade your jet and and try to take on this challenge! Burning Skies is a free, endless retro shmup, that will take you right back to the era of arcade machines, with modernized graphics and gameplay!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290190/extras/03.gif?t=1725479401\" /><br><br>Blast through waves of enemies, improving your jet and equiping it with one of the multiple available weapons!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290190/extras/01.gif?t=1725479401\" /><br><br>Beat the lieutenant Blitz and, mighty war machine, and the army of General Bloodmester!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290190/extras/07.gif?t=1725479401\" /><br><br>Perfect to play when you need just a shot of quick fun! This is a short and free love letter to the 80s arcade games. Inspired by classics like 1942, River Raid, Raiden and more.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290190/extras/05.gif?t=1725479401\" /><br><br>Features<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Beautiful 3D voxel graphics;<br></li><li>Endless procedurally generated gameplay;<br></li><li>Various unique enemies, weapons and a very challenging boss fight;<br></li><li>Original Music</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Unlock Skin #02","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2290190/477a1ed3bf60de98bdccbebb9f234e4b7f9ca67d.jpg"},{"name":"Unlock Skin #03","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2290190/df5b7eda3fb3c28db441c968169ae52d18